high_descs: Turn around completely, walk to the wall, then turn right and walk up to the black chair in the corner of the room.
Pick up the set of keys closest to you on the chair.
Turn to the right and walk over to the left side of the bedside table.
Place the set of keys down on the bedside table.
anns.task_desc: Move a set of keys to the bedside table.

high_descs: Turn around and walk forward to the wall, then turn right and walk to the armchair containing the key chain.
Pick up the key chain from the armchair.
Turn right and walk across the room to the small side table containing the lamp.
Put the key chain on the table, to the left of the remote control.
anns.task_desc: Move a key chain from an armchair to a small side table.

high_descs: Turn around and cross the room and then turn to the right to face the black chair in the corner.
Pick the keys near the edge of the chair up.
Go right and cross the room and then turn to the right to face the lamp on the small round table.
Put the keys on the table.
